title: Texas survives, reaches semis after 2OT classic
description: On the verge of defeat, Texas delivered big plays to escape with a 39-31 double-overtime win over two-TD underdog Arizona State to advance to the CFP semifinals.

title: Sugar Bowl postponed after deadly truck attack
description: The College Football Playoff quarterfinal between Georgia and Notre Dame has been postponed by 24 hours to Thursday following a deadly pickup truck attack in New Orleans.

title: 'No-one can replace Saka' - but Nwaneri, 17, gives Arsenal hope
description: With Bukayo Saka out until March, 17-year-old Ethan Nwaneri shows glimpses against Brentford to give Arsenal hope.

title: Littler beats Aspinall to set up Bunting semi-final
description: Teenager Luke Littler beat his friend Nathan Aspinall 5-2 to set up a semi-final against Stephen Bunting in the PDC World Championship.

title: Littler books Bunting semi with convincing win over Aspinall
description: Luke Littler is through to the World Darts Championship semi-finals after a convincing 5-2 victory over Nathan Aspinall at Alexandra Palace.
